msgid "application_received"
msgstr ""
"<p>Thank you for applying! Your application has been received and will remain active for one (1) year. For new applicants, if your qualifications match the needs of the commission, someone will be in contact with you. For those applying for reappointment, please note that submitting an application does not guarantee your position on the board or commission. We will contact you once a decision has been made regarding your reappointment.</p>\n"
"<p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding your application, please contact Jennifer Crossley, Deputy Clerk of Communications and Outreach in the Office of the City Clerk at <a href=\"tel:812-349-3408\">812-349-3408</a> or <a href=\"mailto:clerk@bloomington.in.gov\">clerk@bloomington.in.gov</a>.</p>"

